Function choose_genera( matrix, n_genera, info generated by LGO-CV ):
  for each LGO-CV:
    cv_accuracy = accuracy returned by LGO-CV
    for each genus g:
  	  count_folds[g] = 0
  	  for each fold of CV:
  	    if fold chooses g then count_folds[g] += 1
  	  accuracy[g] += count_folds[g]*cv_accuracy
  Sort genera into descending order by accuracy[g]	
  return set of the best n_genera genera